                  "content": "LHDN has split the rollout into phases by company turnover. Phase 1 (RM 100M+) is live, Phase 2 (RM 25M+) is live, Phase 3 (RM 150k+) starts 1 July 2025, and Phase 5 for everyone starts 2027.",
