                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "FS2L5",
              "name": "H1",
              "fill": "$ink",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1100,
              "content": "Built for the people we used to be.",
              "lineHeight": 1.05,
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "$font-display",
              "fontSize": 72,
              "fontWeight": "500",
              "letterSpacing": -1.5
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "IyeLw",
          "name": "Founder Story",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 32,
          "padding": [
            64,
            64,
            96,
            64
          ],
          "alignItems": "center",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "d1lhL",
              "name": "Story Body",
              "width": 680,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 24,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "tvkQ4",
                  "name": "Para0",
                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "We started BukuCloud in 2024 after years of feeling the pain of running a Malaysian SME firsthand. One of us ran a 2-outlet F&B shop in KL, the other was an accounts manager at a 30-person firm in Penang.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                  "fontSize": 20
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "v5XsiI",
                  "name": "Para1",
                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Every year, we ran into the same problems. Excel that broke at the worst moments. Accountants charging RM 500 a month for work we should have been able to do ourselves. SQL Account installed on a single PC at the counter, only accessible when that one person was at work. And now — MyInvois LHDN, yet another system that seems designed for big enterprises, not two-person shops like ours.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                  "fontSize": 17
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "gy8sr",
                  "name": "Para2",
                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "We tried every accounting software on the market. Local options were slow and hard to learn. International options didn't understand SST, MyInvois, or how Malaysian SMEs actually work. None of them was made for us.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                  "fontSize": 17
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Esyzt",
                  "name": "Para3",
                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "So we built our own. BukuCloud isn't a SaaS product for everyone. It's specifically for Malaysian SMEs with 5–50 staff who want accounting that works without two weeks of training. MyInvois is in from day one. SST 6% is built in. WhatsApp support, sane pricing, BM language ready when needed.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                  "fontSize": 17
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "RTBke",
                  "name": "Para4",
                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "We hope it helps you the way we wish something like it had helped us.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                  "fontSize": 17
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "IAXPj",
              "name": "Sig",
              "fill": "$ink-muted",
              "content": "— Asyraf & the BukuCloud team",
              "fontFamily": "$font-display",
              "fontSize": 18,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "fontStyle": "italic"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "ScnBL",
          "name": "Mission",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "$surface-alt",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "padding": [
            120,
            64
          ],
          "alignItems": "center",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "sSYxZ",
              "type": "ref",
